snippet.title: Hero of Aethric Trailer - Google Play Store
snippet.description:
Adventure awaits in Hero of Aethric, a nostalgia-fueled MMORPG for iOS and Android. 

Unlock over 75 classes, defeat menacing raids and collect powerful gear as you traverse a pixel art world! Party up with support for up to 4 player co-op. 

Start your adventure today, Hero!
